title: DAEWOO EXT1038 2 Way UK 3Pin Plug 10amp Extension Reel with 10 Metre Heavy-Duty Winding Cable and Safety Cut Out Switch - Assorted colors
features: SAFETY CUT OUT SWITCH - The Pifco extension reel for home/outside garden use features a handy safety cut out function that automatically cuts the power from your extension reel before over-heating for absolute safety
2 WAY SOCKET - The 2 way UK plug outlets are suitable for UK power adapters - The extension lead is ideal for using within your home, offices or even outside in your garden if you need the power

COMPACT DESIGN - The slim, compact and lightweight design allows you transport your extension cable around the house or office with ease while also being able to place it behind your desk or on the floor so it saves space and doesn't get in the way

IDEAL FOR 2 DEVICES - The Pifco extension lead is perfect for when you have 2 appliances that you need powered - For example within your home/office where you need to power the monitor, laptop/desktop, printer or even just for your smartphone

10 METRE LENGTH - This extension cable features a 10 metre length cable, which provides a longer reach your powered devices - Ideal if you're in a large office and need to power your multiple appliances from distance
description: Product Description This Pifco extension reel is perfect for using within your home or outside in your garden - Key features include: • The ideal solution for when you need to connect more than one appliance when there is just one socket available • This extension lead allows you to connect 2 appliances at anyone time for convenience • Safety cut out switch • 10 metre cable length - Ideal for using at home or for outside garden use Box Contains 1 x 10M Extension Reel
